  <data key="d0">"STRUCTURE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Hive roof is the top part of the hive, and it can be affected by vibrations."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-0cae971b0b2192812c441da52ef3cf20</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;HIVE FLOOR&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"STRUCTURE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Hive floor is the bottom part of the hive, and it can be affected by vibrations."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-0cae971b0b2192812c441da52ef3cf20</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;HIVE VENTILATION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"FEATURE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Hive ventilation is a feature that allows air to circulate within the hive, and it can be affected by vibrations."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-0cae971b0b2192812c441da52ef3cf20</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;HIVE INSULATION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"FEATURE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Hive insulation is a feature that helps regulate temperature within the hive, and it can be affected by vibrations."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-0cae971b0b2192812c441da52ef3cf20</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;HIVE VENTILATION HOLES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"FEATURE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Hive ventilation holes are openings that allow air to circulate within the hive, and they can be affected by vibrations."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-0cae971b0b2192812c441da52ef3cf20</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;HIVE ENTRANCE REDUCER&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"TOOL"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Hive entrance reducer is a tool used to control the size of the hive entrance, and it can be affected by vibrations."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-0cae971b0b2192812c441da52ef3cf20</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;HIVE SMOKER&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"TOOL"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Hive smoker is a tool used to calm bees before handling the hive, and it can be affected by vibrations."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-0cae971b0b2192812c441da52ef3cf20</data>
