</node>
<node id="&quot;WOMEN&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Women are performers in burlesque musicals, often playing multiple roles and wearing revealing clothing."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-402377454165587ae1b3b0fcc502ff15</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BUSTLES, LACE, AND MODEST HEMLINES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Bustles, lace, and modest hemlines represent traditional clothing styles that were considered proper for women during that time."</data>
