</node>
<node id="&quot;EDWARD RICE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Edward Rice is a prominent composer and producer of burlesque musicals, known for creating numerous productions on Broadway and touring the United States."&lt;SEP&gt;"Edward Rice is the most important composer and producer of his era, known for producing numerous burlesque musicals on Broadway and touring extensively throughout the United States. He also composed original music for all his scores."</data>
