</node>
<node id="&quot;UNIVERSITY STUDENTS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"University Students refers to the group of six students, four of whom were dropped off at Angmagssalik and two who conducted scientific studies on board and on shore."&lt;SEP&gt;"University Students refers to the group of six students, four of whom were dropped off at Angmagssalik and two who conducted scientific studies on board and on shore.")</data>
