</node>
<node id="&quot;INUIT&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Inuit refers to the indigenous people of Greenland among whom some university students lived for a year as part of an ethnographic study."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-4a044eb6c9ea43a457fda3a5ae087892</data>
</node>
