<node id="&quot;DANCE TRAINING&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Dance Training involves various techniques such as breathing and muscle control, specifically focusing on clavicular breathing and abdominal breathing."&lt;SEP&gt;"Dance Training is a form of physical training that enhances a singer's performance capabilities, particularly in music theater."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-ec12e59f09a5549285ad21ffed9bbbd6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-df3a4ad39eb32af1c4e7f021a096b02d</data>
