<node id="&quot;BREATHING TECHNIQUES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Breathing Techniques are fundamental for music theater singing and are covered in NATS resources."&lt;SEP&gt;"Breathing Techniques are specific methods used in singing and dancing to control breath and support vocal production."&lt;SEP&gt;"Breathing Techniques include both clavicular breathing for dancers and abdominal breathing for singers, which are different methods for better control and performance."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-ec12e59f09a5549285ad21ffed9bbbd6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4ee81c7295f7a8aec355921dc084183c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-df3a4ad39eb32af1c4e7f021a096b02d</data>
