<edge source="&quot;BEES&quot;" target="&quot;HIVE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">62.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Bees are located within the hive and are sensitive to movements and vibrations near the hive."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bees are the members of the colony that work within the hive, performing various tasks such as foraging and pollination."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bees live and work within a Hive, and their behavior is influenced by the actions of a Person interacting with the Hive."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bees live and work within the hive, performing tasks necessary for the colony's survival and productivity."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bees live and work within the hive, which provides them with shelter and a place to function."</data>
