  <data key="d4">12.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Hook-wired foundation uses wire to guide bees, while wedge-style top bars provide structural support."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-fd2ef96a08268bf831497844fff694b4</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
