  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Frame wire is used to fasten wire-reinforced foundation into frames, ensuring it does not bend or buckle prematurely."&lt;SEP&gt;"Frame wire is used to secure wire-reinforced foundation into the frames."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-075e0d9993c009051cdcd78e585e5e63</data>
