  <data key="d5">"Worker Bees are part of the Colony, working together to maintain the hive and ensure its survival."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-d5b1917950dbf98fe0b5ce38e219280a</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;WORKER BEE&quot;" target="&quot;STIMULUS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Worker Bees respond to various Stimuli, such as Movement or Approach, which can affect their behavior."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-d5b1917950dbf98fe0b5ce38e219280a</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;WORKER BEE&quot;" target="&quot;MOVEMENT&quot;">
  <data key="d4">6.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Worker Bees can be affected by Movement, such as the approach of a beekeeper, which can cause them to react."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-d5b1917950dbf98fe0b5ce38e219280a</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;WORKER BEE&quot;" target="&quot;APPROACH&quot;">
  <data key="d4">6.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Worker Bees can react to an Approach, which can be a form of Stimulus."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-d5b1917950dbf98fe0b5ce38e219280a</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;WORKER BEE&quot;" target="&quot;YOUNG BEE DEVELOPMENT&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Worker Bees play a crucial role in the Young Bee Development process within the Hive."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-d5b1917950dbf98fe0b5ce38e219280a</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;WORKER BEE&quot;" target="&quot;PLANT REPRODUCTION&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
