  <data key="d4">34.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Debtors have a relationship with Prepetition Agents where they must promptly notify them about any Proposed Alternative Transaction, indicating a communication channel for financial dealings."&lt;SEP&gt;"Debtors must provide notice to the Prepetition Agents and consult with them regarding Revised Supporting Lender Proposals."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-6b4933e28419676b4dc2c84fef33d751&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-73e41d4fce5a979254140bea80d946f2</data>
